name: ChikinCoin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Chikin is the front page of the decentralized chikin society, ChikinCoin (CKC) it is driving force. 
More than 26 billion chikin currently living, pecking and eating, and yet none of them have access to basic financial services.
